    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Rewiring my brain: APL and J]]></title>
    <link href="http://citizen428.net/blog/2010/08/16/rewiring-my-brain-apl-and-j/"/>
    <updated>2010-08-16T00:00:00+02:00</updated>
